    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"479359\">@Michael Stoll</span> Can you please add something about <strong>Tonelli's theorem</strong> to the docstring of <code>summable_prod_of_nonneg</code>? I immediately thought of this result by name when I started reading this thread.</p>",
